As I promised earlier, I'm gonna list out the projects that were successfully launched in less than 48 hours in Estonia. I have omitted some projects that I deemed are not applicable to the situation back home.
• Real-time covid19 tracker with heatmaps
• Workforce sharing platform
• Medical volunteer management database
• A platform to connect people at risk (for ex. the elderly) with volunteers.
• A delivery service for groceries
• Self assessment app
• Corona bot to answer questions people might have
